text: Rauch Partido is a partido in the centre-east of Buenos Aires Province in Argentina. The provincial subdivision has a population of about 14,000 inhabitants in an area of , and its capital city is Rauch. ==Settlements== *Rauch: 12.495 inhabitants *Miranda: 80 inhabitants *Egaña: 44 inhabitants *Colman: 27 inhabitants ==External links== * municipal site (Spanish) * federal site (Spanish) Category:1865 establishments in Argentina Category:Partidos of Buenos Aires Province
